metadata.name: F A S T P E P Ξ #1
metadata.description:
An icon.
A timeless icon. A meme born out of a relentless pursuit of a dream. A deep green, short-bodied, tailless amphibian that broke boundaries and defied convention. Now, it is (again) leaving the pond and embarking on a new journey, steered by your passions.

Owning one of 2363 FASTPEPΞs gives you access to a new world of froggery where the rewards are unreal and maybe/maybe not that special, depends on what you´re used to really.


A community of like-minded pioneers.
Connect with like-minded creators and thought-leaders from the Web3 world at your own peril. 
To co-create the future of fast-moving frogs together.


There's a roadmap in the glove box, there are milestones down the road. If the collections sells out, we´re buying a real Porsche 911, fitting it with KELLY-MOSS Safari / Dakar Rally kit, and painting it Pepe color. We might even raffle it out to the token holders.
